  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de WebKitGTK</title>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Instalação de <application>WebKitGTK</application></bridgehead>



    <!--
    <para>

      Fix an issue causing a crash viewing some web pages:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../webkitgtk-&webkitgtk-version;-upstream_fix-1.patch</userinput></screen>
-->
<para>
      Install <application>WebKitGTK</application> by running the following
commands:
    </para>

<screen revision="systemd"><userinput>mkdir -vp build &amp;&amp;
cd        build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release  \
      -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr \
      -DCMAKE_SKIP_RPATH=ON       \
      -DPORT=GTK                  \
      -DLIB_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/lib  \
      -DUSE_LIBHYPHEN=OFF         \
      -DENABLE_GAMEPAD=OFF        \
      -DENABLE_MINIBROWSER=ON     \
      -DENABLE_DOCUMENTATION=OFF  \
      -DUSE_WOFF2=OFF             \
      -DUSE_WPE_RENDERER=ON       \
      -DENABLE_BUBBLEWRAP_SANDBOX=OFF \
      -Wno-dev -G Ninja ..        &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

<screen revision="sysv"><userinput>mkdir -vp build &amp;&amp;
cd        build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release  \
      -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr \
      -DCMAKE_SKIP_RPATH=ON       \
      -DPORT=GTK                  \
      -DLIB_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/lib  \
      -DUSE_LIBHYPHEN=OFF         \
      -DENABLE_GAMEPAD=OFF        \
      -DENABLE_MINIBROWSER=ON     \
      -DENABLE_DOCUMENTATION=OFF  \
      -DUSE_WOFF2=OFF             \
      -DUSE_WPE_RENDERER=ON       \
      -DENABLE_JOURNALD_LOG=OFF   \
      -DENABLE_BUBBLEWRAP_SANDBOX=OFF \
      -Wno-dev -G Ninja ..        &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not have a working test suite. However, there is a usable
basic graphical web browser in the build directory,
<application>build/bin/MiniBrowser</application>. If launching it fails,
there is a problem with the build.
    </para>



